      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ticketmaster-may-have-broken-uk-law-with-platinum-oasis-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦的监管机构说，Ticketmaster可能通过出售一些OASIS音乐会门票的违反英国法律，价格为其他座位的2.5倍，而无需告知公众的定价计划。]]></description>
